> That's right, gift**s**, plural, because I decied to make a whole bunch of bonus gifts in addition to my main gift. **Five** gifts in total, in fact!
>
> Alright, let's get started.
>
> (The drawings look a bit crunchy, so if you click on them, they should appear in a new tab where you can see them un-crunched)
 _

[[tabview]]
[[tab I wonder if that budget increase request was approved... (gift for JukeShoes)]]
[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/art%3A2024-art-exchange-miss-lapis/AE_JukeShoes_text.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/art%3A2024-art-exchange-miss-lapis/AE_JukeShoes_text.png"]]

> [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/forum/t-16984471/13th-annual-art-exchange#post-6728625 I would really like] some art for my Blistering Budget tale
>
> Have fun please!

This was my main gift! An illustration for [[[blistering-budget|]]]. Jeez, I wonder if their budget increase request //was// approved? I improvised with all the character designs, I hope Juke won't mind h

[[collapsible show="View version without speech bubbles." hide="Hide version without speech bubbles."]]
[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/art%3A2024-art-exchange-miss-lapis/AE_JukeShoes.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/art%3A2024-art-exchange-miss-lapis/AE_JukeShoes.png"]]
[[/collapsible]]
[[/tab]]

[[tab Cornered from all sides (bonus for Sugarush)]]
[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/art%3A2024-art-exchange-miss-lapis/sugar_bonus_.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/art%3A2024-art-exchange-miss-lapis/sugar_bonus_.png"]]

I played bingo, like [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/forum/t-16984471/13th-annual-art-exchange#post-6729243 Sugar's AE request] specified, and chose the row of "the machine is a computer or building / a pathetic man is there / girls and machines / deeply romantic / the machine is evil". This is my finest drawing yet and it's also the one where I tried out gradient maps for the first time. So much fun

(this was going to have a companion tale but unfortunately life got in the way. It is what it is! I hope you will enjoy the drawing on its own regardless)
[[/tab]]

[[tab Lettuce, sugar, butter, baguette, annnnddddd a refreshing can of energy drink (Hedvig is just happy to be shopping on her own again while Hedara is amazed empresses now can shop on their own (and she also wants a sip of the energy drink)) or, Women Be Shopping (bonus for Rounderhouse)]]
[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/art%3A2024-art-exchange-miss-lapis/bonus_rounder_2.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/art%3A2024-art-exchange-miss-lapis/bonus_rounder_2.png"]]

> Hedvig Nussbaum going grocery shopping.

Hedvig goes grocery shopping, as the [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/forum/t-16984471/13th-annual-art-exchange#post-6730402 request] specified (and has Hedara tag along). Wears a headscarf to hide her wings and because I thought Hedvig in a headscarf would be cute so I just HAD to draw it. Timeline-wise this drawing takes place after [[[heresy|]]].[[footnote]] At this point I discovered my laptop has pen pressure... [[/footnote]]

[[footnoteblock]]
[[/tab]]

[[tab When spending time with your deer gf feels like spending time in seventh heaven (bonus for Astersquill)]]
[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/art%3A2024-art-exchange-miss-lapis/bonus_aster.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/art%3A2024-art-exchange-miss-lapis/bonus_aster.png"]]

> Something holiday related staring Hana (of SCP-6317 and other, assorted works) and Meri (of SCP-8166 and other assorted works). Romance is fine, a holiday situation is fine, I just want something with them set around the holidays.

I don't really have much commentary for this drawing, other than this was made for Aster's [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/forum/t-16984471/13th-annual-art-exchange#post-6728601 request] for fun!
[[/tab]]

[[tab I know there were no screens in Amoni-Ram but let me dream or, Two kitty cats taking a nap together (bonus #2 for Rounderhouse]]
[[image https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/art%3A2024-art-exchange-miss-lapis/bonus_rounder_text.png link="*https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/art%3A2024-art-exchange-miss-lapis/bonus_rounder_text.png"]]

> Ansool and Bileath adopt(ed) a cat.

Jeez, Rounder, how come mom lets you have TWO bonus gifts? I couldn't resist this excuse that presented itself to make a drawing of [[[scp-8600|my very own]]] [[[fratricide|pookie]]], so here. Enjoy!

